title: At least 260 bodies recovered after attack on music festival
description: At least 260 bodies were found after Hamas targeted a music festival in Israel as part of its incursion, rescuers have said.

title: People in southern Israeli city left in shock after Hamas incursion
description: Surrounded by destruction, and in the midst of a few local people dazed and frankly in shock after the events of Saturday and Hamas's attack, I prepared to leave the city of Sderot.

title: Israel has been caught unawares and now faces a perilous challenge
description: "Where have you been? Where was everybody?" The questions were being screamed at soldiers on a highway by a man stricken with grief.

title: 'Terrorists are in my bedroom': The haunting messages helpless relatives received after Hamas abductions
description: "Everything I have in my life - my family - is missing," Gaya Kalderon tells Sky News.

title: 12 hours in 'hell': Man describes moment Hamas militants stormed his home
description: A British-Israeli citizen and his wife have told of their 12 hour ordeal locked in a bomb-proof safe room as Hamas militants set their house on fire and gunfights erupted around them.

title: British man serving in Israeli army killed in Hamas attack
description: A British man who was serving in the Israeli army has been killed in an attack by Hamas militants.

title: Policeman shoots dead two Israelis at Egyptian tourist site
description: Two Israeli tourists and their Egyptian guide have been shot dead at a tourist site in Alexandria, according to Israel's foreign ministry.

title: British citizen missing after Hamas attack on music festival
description: A British citizen is missing after Hamas attacked a music festival in Israel, the country's embassy in the UK has told Sky News.

title: Briton missing after Hamas attack on music festival
description: A British man is missing after Hamas attacked a music festival in Israel, the country's embassy in the UK has told Sky News.

title: Almost 2,000 dead after Afghanistan earthquakes, says Taliban
description: Almost 2.000 people have died after earthquakes in Afghanistan on Saturday, according to the Taliban.

title: Netanyahu warns people to leave Gaza as he vows to reduce parts of the territory 'into rubble'
description: Israel's prime minister has warned people living in Gaza to leave the area as he vowed to reduce parts of the territory "into rubble" in revenge for a "black day".

title: An astonishing unravelling of a situation that's long been forgotten, ignored, or tolerated. What next?
description: It was 2.30am in Washington DC when White House officials were first alerted to a situation which will come to represent a truly bloody turning point.
